@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (tmp / wp.exp((v2 + 0.08 / tmp + 0.86)))
    v2 = 0.02
    v0 = v2
    v1 = wp.exp(v2)
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v0 + 0.26)) / (0.77 / wp.sin(tmp + 0.26)))
    tmp = wp.exp(0.97)
    data[tid] = v0
